  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heroic icon of English ballads clashes with the forces of the nefarious Sheriff of Nottingham in <strong>Robin Hood: Sherwood Defenders</strong>! Engage in <strong>raid defenses</strong> as you <strong>fend off wave after wave</strong> of incoming enemies both by <strong>placing structures</strong> and having Robin himself <strong>leap into the thick of the fight</strong>! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Defense </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up a variety of defenses to prepare in advance of the enemy fighters' arrival. <strong>Towers, walls, traps, and gates</strong> all provide nasty surprises for those who would seek to fuel the Sheriff's greed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hire additional soldiers</strong> to man the stronghold you create and help defeat the invaders before they take out its central structure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/18ee2b0b101737ca26752ba6331ae586.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/18ee2b0b101737ca26752ba6331ae586.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/18ee2b0b101737ca26752ba6331ae586.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Economy </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you'll need resources of your own if you're to withstand the growing onslaught, so don't forget to place <strong>production buildings</strong> alongside fortifications and then balance them to prevail. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the right <strong>resource income</strong>, you'll be able to afford <strong>upgrades</strong> to your current buildings and make them more effective in their purpose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c065ecd91b9906ef27bbfcdd628bad78.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c065ecd91b9906ef27bbfcdd628bad78.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c065ecd91b9906ef27bbfcdd628bad78.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robin Hood takes charge of defending the homes of his most loyal allies in the fight against the Sheriff but he can also put his legendary <strong>archery</strong> and <strong>swordsmanship</strong> skills to use in the fights. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a wave of hostile soldiers appears, stand side-by-side with the other brave defenders! The <strong>different unit types</strong> among your allies and enemies have their strengths and weaknesses, so make the right choices!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c8924e345a6a4ad1e6b70c687c54f4ce.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c8924e345a6a4ad1e6b70c687c54f4ce.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c8924e345a6a4ad1e6b70c687c54f4ce.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Rewards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you succeed in battles, you make yourself ready to <strong>move on to a new area </strong>and <strong>unlock rewards</strong> in the form of new buildings, new defenses, new warriors, and even new arrows for Robin to use in the fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/4a956015a9609475bb71fc9e52b65038.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/4a956015a9609475bb71fc9e52b65038.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/4a956015a9609475bb71fc9e52b65038.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heroic icon of English ballads clashes with the forces of the nefarious Sheriff of Nottingham in <strong>Robin Hood: Sherwood Defenders</strong>! Engage in <strong>raid defenses</strong> as you <strong>fend off wave after wave</strong> of incoming enemies both by <strong>placing structures</strong> and having Robin himself <strong>leap into the thick of the fight</strong>! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Defense </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up a variety of defenses to prepare in advance of the enemy fighters' arrival. <strong>Towers, walls, traps, and gates</strong> all provide nasty surprises for those who would seek to fuel the Sheriff's greed. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hire additional soldiers</strong> to man the stronghold you create and help defeat the invaders before they take out its central structure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/18ee2b0b101737ca26752ba6331ae586.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/18ee2b0b101737ca26752ba6331ae586.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/18ee2b0b101737ca26752ba6331ae586.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Economy </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, you'll need resources of your own if you're to withstand the growing onslaught, so don't forget to place <strong>production buildings</strong> alongside fortifications and then balance them to prevail. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the right <strong>resource income</strong>, you'll be able to afford <strong>upgrades</strong> to your current buildings and make them more effective in their purpose.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c065ecd91b9906ef27bbfcdd628bad78.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c065ecd91b9906ef27bbfcdd628bad78.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c065ecd91b9906ef27bbfcdd628bad78.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Fight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Robin Hood takes charge of defending the homes of his most loyal allies in the fight against the Sheriff but he can also put his legendary <strong>archery</strong> and <strong>swordsmanship</strong> skills to use in the fights. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a wave of hostile soldiers appears, stand side-by-side with the other brave defenders! The <strong>different unit types</strong> among your allies and enemies have their strengths and weaknesses, so make the right choices!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c8924e345a6a4ad1e6b70c687c54f4ce.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c8924e345a6a4ad1e6b70c687c54f4ce.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/c8924e345a6a4ad1e6b70c687c54f4ce.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The Rewards</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you succeed in battles, you make yourself ready to <strong>move on to a new area </strong>and <strong>unlock rewards</strong> in the form of new buildings, new defenses, new warriors, and even new arrows for Robin to use in the fight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/4a956015a9609475bb71fc9e52b65038.poster.avif?t=1762260788\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/4a956015a9609475bb71fc9e52b65038.webm?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037660/extras/4a956015a9609475bb71fc9e52b65038.mp4?t=1762260788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
